{
  "texts": [
    "Image Analysis and Artificial Intelligence.",
    "Artificial Intelligence (AI) is not a novel idea.",
    "Renowned intellectuals like Leonardo Da Vinci [124] attempted to build automata that mimicked human actions.",
    "These days, it appears that this is already the case.",
    "Though there are many self-adjusting intelligent systems already, AI has grown exponentially, particularly in the field of health informatics [84]."
  ]
}